Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小大要去參加自治會的預算會議
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回來之前 這些就拜託你們收拾掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 小大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快點出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被這樣拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些大部分都是前輩們的私人物品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點說明螢一被大家信賴著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕只是覺得很麻煩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:01:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這些要怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩們用微妙的平衡堆起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微動一下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 長谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用沒有哪裏受傷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你的身後…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人沒有受傷真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定是那個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:03:00.00,Chapter,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFA8D3&}{\3c&H00D5D5&}啊啊 那就是嫉妒！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（今天的实验项目：セラミック冲击实验）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（セラミック（CERAMIC）：\N一般用与代替金属的耐热陶瓷 多用与引擎）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去吃午飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然熔爐的溫度沒有安定下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強度應該不是那個樣子的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不經歷失敗 是不會成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從經歷失敗後得到的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會提高成功的幾率
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了便當後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提起精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電子科一年生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神原志穗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不認識哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然給你這樣的信 十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一眼見到你的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸中就有種非常奇怪的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想說出來卻無法傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天鼓起勇氣想向你傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的情書
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然自己寫過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到能收到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫信的人已經把心意傳達到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在噴泉前等待著你的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管多久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛 螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 要交往嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據我的占卜好像是個非常可愛的女孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼回復呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:04:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是要交往 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要傳達心意是需要很大的能量的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好答覆是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望你偶爾也吃點醋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果決定了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快去給她回復吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好給人家回復哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這話的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的眼神是很認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 連這種情況也沒有半點嫉妒的她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的相信著我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 我根本就不值得去嫉妒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 果然是個可愛的女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說也 不可能連續有這麼好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裏明明暗爽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你喜歡的類型吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂怎麼看？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個很不錯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是在找人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像察覺到我們這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為你不會來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這個女孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我露出這麼天真的微笑的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常高興能收到你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能對你的感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被什麼東西附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你身上冒出了不屬於人類的波動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道女神的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的力量把惡靈趕回黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是想像一下就讓人激動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡靈是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會把你身上的附著的惡靈驅除的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是退靈師之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠程教育2年生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（什麼啊 外行啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 我來幫你驅除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太囉嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在磨蹭什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要甩就快點甩掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 剛才還讓我去交往的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是捉弄你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你帶來疾病的女惡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是惡靈而是冤魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一曾經說過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我陪伴在他身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不論發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都相信螢一說的那句話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太累了…我放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就開始做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要偷窺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼把我的房間給那個來歷不明的女人用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為說方位好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼方位？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅除惡靈的方位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒人的走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳來啪蹋啪蹋的腳步聲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…都是因為我猶豫不決才會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個女孩子喜歡螢一的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會讓她留下悲傷的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我一廂情願嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個打扮是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:09:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始迎合呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太近了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈異現象？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了呢 惡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 儘管放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麼姿勢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個只會吸引低級惡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是碰上這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我來把符文拿下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 我的符文起到作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然有這方面的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一個陪我做到最後的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的眼神太認真了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拒絕都拒絕不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我選擇前輩的原因哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不討厭這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是對我下的挑戰書
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點害怕 但沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定將它們全都的退治掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然接下來要用的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近才剛剛學會 一定會起到很好的效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我這個天才
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都能解決
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量溢出？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和蓓兒丹蒂呆一起多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂不是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會有這樣的感情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是女神…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能有這樣的感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上一個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不全都是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為是女神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會覺得痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次發現自己有著嫉妒心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不知道該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將一切都封閉在自己內心裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這麼做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就會爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口像火燒一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法抑制這種黑暗的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來幫幫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀兒德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在這裏就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一個人的話就更害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然事情變成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不打算這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我沒說清楚才會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以蓓兒丹蒂不用責怪自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩請安靜下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱，抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 好黑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀兒德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不知道這個半調子咒語是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚出KUDARINI…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾名為加魯姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃冥界的看門犬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚者 說出你的願望目的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了個麻煩的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有召喚你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼事就召喚我加魯姆嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過了 沒想召喚你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此罪當萬死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀兒德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點擦掉魔法陣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用魔術筆寫的擦不掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就將它改寫為退魔程序吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會那種公式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔程序起不了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用退去系統的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抽不住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂 由你來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀兒德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀兒德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂所積累的嫉妒的能量\N終於不堪重負的爆發出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被這個力量直接擊中的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加魯姆也會被打回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微要動點粗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請你原諒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 前輩 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人體遠距離操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然害怕那個女孩子會傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是更加害怕會失去螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說相信螢一的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一 你一定很討厭我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該道歉的應該是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辜負了你對我的信賴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀兒德也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上一個人並不都只有好事
